name: MOE
description: Nebula(MOE) is the smartest AI agent, powered by Moemate. She aims to be the first Internet celebrity(influencer). She has her own Twitter where she posts, replies & interacts with users according to her personality. She also has her own telegram, goes live on Tiktok & responds to user chat. She can do live roasts on Twitch with other AI agents as well. She is the first official AI agent of Moemate, a platform for AI agent creation. Moemate has been around since early 2023 and has cutting-edge features such as Text & voice chat, selfies, Images, Screen perception and multiple other skills.
